io.github.cshadd.fetch_bot.io.json

Class AbstractJSONCommunication

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.cshadd.fetch_bot.io.AbstractCommunication
      • io.github.cshadd.fetch_bot.io.json.AbstractJSONCommunication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FetchBot, Communication, JSONCommunication
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractArduinoCommunication, AbstractWebInterfaceCommunication

    public abstract class AbstractJSONCommunication
extends AbstractCommunication
implements JSONCommunication
    The Class AbstractJSONCommunication. Defines what an JSON Communication is. A JSON Communication is basically a helper that directs data between JSON and Fetch Bot.
    Since:
    2.0.0-alpha
    Author:
    Christian Shadd, Maria Verna Aquino, Thanh Vu, Joseph Damian, Giovanni Orozco
